{"TopicId":216884,"ForumId":120,"TopicTitle":"Make fairings transparent","CreatedByName":"Vortygont","CreatedById":223549,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-26T13:44:24Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Vortygont","CreatedById":223549,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-26T13:44:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI came up with this idea when I wanted to edit my spacecraft under x2 fairing. Problem that I didn\u0027t see craft because fairing blocked my view. Fairing opening depends on camera and cursor positions, and this system doesn\u0027t work well. For example half of x2 fairing still blocks view, while other half jerks sharply and blocks view if you zoom very much. If fairings were transparent, these problems would be solved easily and craft editing would become much comfortable\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cocoscacao","CreatedById":225696,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-26T14:24:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere should be an eye icon when you hover on fairing that toggles transparency\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vortygont","CreatedById":223549,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-26T17:49:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224277133\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022216884\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221682519062\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022225696\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022cocoscacao\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, cocoscacao said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere should be an eye icon when you hover on fairing that toggles transparency\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere is no transparency, it just open one half of fairing in 2x case, and it doesn\u0027t become transparent.\u00A0In other cases, the view is better because most of the fairing is ajar\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022950KerbalSpaceProgram22.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022118.46\u0022 height=\u0022462\u0022 width=\u0022390\u0022 src=\u0022https://u.cubeupload.com/Vortygont/950KerbalSpaceProgram22.png\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"pandaman","CreatedById":130621,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-26T17:56:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224277133\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022216884\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221682519062\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022225696\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022cocoscacao\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, cocoscacao said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere should be an eye icon when you hover on fairing that toggles transparency\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh, so that\u0027s what it\u0027s supposed to do.\u00A0\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:joy:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/joy.png\u0022 title=\u0022:joy:\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cocoscacao","CreatedById":225696,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-26T18:00:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224277173\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022216884\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221682531363\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022223549\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Vortygont\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n11 minutes ago, Vortygont said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere is no transparency\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGah, you\u0027re correct. My wishes clouded my memory. I have no idea why fairings (and making them) is changed. KSP 1 had a perfect implementation.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/130621-pandaman/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022130621\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/130621-pandaman/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@pandaman\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0Nah, my bad. It just opens half of the fairing.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-04-26T18:02:06Z\u0022 title=\u002204/26/2023 06:02  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EApril 26, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by cocoscacao\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"GalileOh-No","CreatedById":228006,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-26T22:24:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe engine plate fairings do have transparency, might explain the mix-up \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/225696-cocoscacao/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022225696\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/225696-cocoscacao/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@cocoscacao\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\nAnybody else that can confirm it\u0027s not just me on that?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vortygont","CreatedById":223549,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-27T05:46:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224277263\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022216884\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221682547844\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022228006\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022GalileOh-No\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 hours ago, GalileOh-No said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnybody else that can confirm it\u0027s not just me on that?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes, eye icon on engine plate fairings toggle transparency, unlike ordinary fairings\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jup","CreatedById":184597,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-27T07:56:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224277320\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022216884\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221682574411\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022223549\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Vortygont\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, Vortygont said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes, eye icon on engine plate fairings toggle transparency, unlike ordinary fairings\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0Which means that it\u0027s doable. Sweet.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Revengist","CreatedById":229010,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-05-13T13:37:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can toggle on and off fairings and they keep their shape\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}